<HEADLINE>Boys bailed in pistol inquiry</HEADLINE>
<EDITION>2</EDITION>
<PAGE>7</PAGE>
<RECORDNO>974667815</RECORDNO>
<TEXT>
Two 15-year-old boys were released on police bail yesterday after a starting
pistol was discharged at an off-duty police officer's car in Milton Keynes,
Buckinghamshire, on Christmas Eve.
A police spokesman said: ``There is the possibility of court proceedings. The
boys have been released pending further inquiries.''
